title: Middlekauff: Wentz/Foles brewing QB controversy; CFB Playoff preview and picks
itunes:title: Middlekauff: Wentz/Foles brewing QB controversy; CFB Playoff preview and picks
description:
Subscribe here to the 3 and Out with John Middlekauff Podcast https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/3-and-out-with-john-middlekauff/id1352730623?mt=2. Middlekauff looks at the brewing QB controversy in Philly between Nick Foles and Carson Wentz, previews the College Football Playoff and gives his picks, and answers listener questions in Middlekauff's Mailbag.
